name: Heliantone Gem
description: Heliantone version of Rainbow Gem. Heliantone is the name of tattooing style created by Murat Atimtay which is a result of generative art algorithm. The algorithm was developed in order to create visually stunning dotwork tattoos. In 2019 he exhibited the style and was awarded at Frankfurt Tattoo Convention | https://www.instagram.com/muratatimtay/ and other works on https://linktr.ee/atimtakus @atimtay
